      • callIsJSONFormat

        public RetrofitClient.Builder callIsJSONFormat()
        todo note! this is breaking something where using this ignores the headers listed within the interface method! Simple setter method for those who are too lazy to make a hashmap containing "Content-Type", "application/json" as headers. Just call this and it will set it. Keep in mind this will replace other headers you have in place so call this before you make any other header alterations (IE with a client id or auth token)
